column5: This morning went to Sibbald point park to see the  blast off of the Bass pro open at lake Simcoe,  60 boats,was foggy but everything went well, no pics yet.
not too windy should be big bags of fish
the wind was calm, i will go later to see the  weight in
1st Place was 29.22LBS and second place 28.60.  Awesome bags of fish!!!!!
Awesome weights. Must have gotten ugly out there this afternoon with that wind coming up. Wonder when the full results will be posted. Wonder if bigfish cracked the 8 pound mark.
Wow Huge Bags 29.20 lbs! Still haven't cracked the 30 lb bag but Simcoe in the fall is the place to do it! Does anyone know where the results will be posted or even the top ten weights were?
